god script



JOBS

letterer to write text
illustrators for illuminated manuscripts
shepherd to raise sheep for vellum
bookbinder to create books


	
breakpoints at 5, 10, 20, 50 etc monks for new facilities


UI

Counters

	counter for words written. 
	counter for books written

Buttons
	write word
	hire monk
	bind book
	create vellum sheet


Windows

1. generated text
2. monastery view
3. worker allocation
4. monastery updates